<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8389471>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Phylogram generated fromBayesian analysis based oncombined LSU andITS sequence.Bootstrap support values forBayesian posterior probabilities (BYPP) equal to or greater than 0.80, maximum likelihood (ML) and maximum parsimony (MP) analyzable to higher than 50% are indicated at the nodes, respectively. Ex-type strains are in bold. The newly generated sequences are in red." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8389471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8389473>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Digitopodium citri (ZHKU 23-0005, holotype). a, b Colony on PDA after three weeks of incubation under 28 ℃—front and reverse. c Mycelial coils. d Conidial chains. e, h, i Conidiophores, conidiogenous cell, primary ramoconidia. f Chlamydospores. g Immature conidiophores." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8389473/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

